nline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596940/extras/ec0edc49ebbbb65b575c9b505943edd9.poster.avif?t=1664802614\" width=636 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596940/extras/ec0edc49ebbbb65b575c9b505943edd9.webm?t=1664802614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596940/extras/ec0edc49ebbbb65b575c9b505943edd9.mp4?t=1664802614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596940/extras/5d0a46dac18f9d6340513e2ff6b03ff2.webp?t=1664802614\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br>So, choose which hero to be – Ryan, Combo Panda, Alpha Lexa, or Gus the Gummy Gator – and jump into Ryan’s World. Invite a friend or grown-up to play with you in local two-player mode. And try exciting games like Spaceship Flight and The Floor is Lava. Can you defeat Dark Titan and his fiendish allies?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596940/extras/207b89953b5ea4a151639e17ca5fce7b.poster.avif?t=1664802614\" width=636 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596940/extras/207b89953b5ea4a151639e17ca5fce7b.webm?t=1664802614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1596940/extras/207b89953b5ea4a151639e17ca5fce7b.mp4?t=1664802614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>FEATURES<br>•\tCHOOSE YOUR CHARACTER – Be Ryan, Combo Panda, Alpha Lexa, or Gus the Gummy Gator<br>•\tTEAM UP – Play together in local 2-player mode<br>•\tPLAY MINIGAMES – Including Bulls Eye, Spaceship Flight, The Floor is Lava and Fire at will!<br>•\tPOWER UP! – Eat Moe’s pizza to become invincible, and more!<br>•\tCOLLECT AND CUSTOMIZE – Unlock and buy amazing new costumes for your character",
